{"ID":270102, "Text":"<div class=\"page\"><div class=\"pageNum\"><a name=\"102\"><\/a><div class=\"prev\"><a href=\"stpjs101.html\">Prev<\/a><\/div><div class=\"next\"><a href=\"stpjs103.html\">Next<\/a><\/div>\n\t\t\t    STPJS 102<\/div>\n  <p class=\"cont\">great price, went and sold all that he had, and bought it.&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">1<\/span> The Saints again work after this example.\n  See men traveling to find places for Zion and her stakes or remnants, who, when they find the place\n  for Zion, or the pearl of great price, straightway sell that they have, and buy it.<span class=\"footRef\">2<\/span><\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">The Net Cast in the Sea<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">&ldquo;Again, the Kingdom of Heaven is like unto a net that was cast into the sea, and gathered of\n  every kind, which when it was full they drew to shore, and sat down, and gathered the good into\n  vessels, but cast the bad away.&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">3<\/span> For the work of this pattern, behold the seed of Joseph,<span class=\"footRef\">4<\/span> spreading\n  forth the Gospel net upon the face of the earth,<span class=\"footRef\">5<\/span> gathering of every kind, that the good may be saved\n  in vessels prepared for that purpose, and the angels will take care of the bad.<span class=\"footRef\">6<\/span> So shall it be at the\n  end of the world&mdash;the angels shall come forth and sever the wicked from among the just, and cast\n  them into the furnace of fire, and there shall be wailing and gnashing of teeth.<span class=\"footRef\">7<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">&ldquo;Jesus saith unto them, Have ye understood all these things? They say unto Him, Yea, Lord.&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">8<\/span>\n  And we say, yea, Lord; and well might they say, yea, Lord; for these things are so plain and so\n  glorious, that every Saint in that last days must respond with a hearty Amen to them.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">&ldquo;Then said He unto them, therefore every scribe which is instructed in the kingdom of heaven,\n  is like unto a man that is an householder, which bringeth forth out of his treasure things that are new\n  and old.&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">9<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">For the works of this example, see the Book of Mormon coming forth out of the treasure of the\n  heart.<span class=\"footRef\">10<\/span> Also the covenants given to the Latter-day Saints, also the translation of the Bible&mdash;thus\n  bringing forth out of the heart things new and old,<span class=\"footRef\">11<\/span> thus answering to three measures of meal<span class=\"footRef\">12<\/span>\n  undergoing the purifying touch by a revelation of Jesus Christ,<span class=\"footRef\">13<\/span> and the ministering of angels,<span class=\"footRef\">14<\/span> who\n  have already commenced this work in the last days, which will answer to the leaven which leavened\n  the whole lump.<span class=\"footRef\">15<\/span> Amen.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">So I close, but shall continue the subject in another number.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">In the bonds of the New and Everlasting Covenant,<\/p>\n  <p class=\"right\">JOSEPH SMITH, JUN.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"right\">&mdash;Messenger and Advocate, Dec. 1835, also DHC 2:264-272.<\/p>\n  <div class=\"footnotes\">\n    <div class=\"footnote\">1. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108041\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108041)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108041)\">Matt. 13:45-46<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">2. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113934\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113934)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113934)\">D&amp;C 48:4<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114052\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114052)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114052)\">D&amp;C 57:2-4<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">3. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108043\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108043)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108043)\">Matt. 13:47-48<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">4. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112349\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112349)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112349)\">Alma 46:23<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112588\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112588)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112588)\">3 Ne. 10:17<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112918\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112918)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112918)\">Ether 13:7<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">5. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106208\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106208)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106208)\">Ex. 33:16<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110900\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110900)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110900)\">1 Ne. 1:11<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113530\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113530)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113530)\">D&amp;C 29:18<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116749\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116749)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116749)\">Moses 3:5<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">6. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108044\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108044)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108044)\">Matt. 13:49-50<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">7. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108038\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108038)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108038)\">Matt. 13:41-42<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">8. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108045\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108045)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108045)\">Matt. 13:51<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">9. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108046\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108046)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108046)\">Matt. 13:52<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">10. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107982\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107982)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107982)\">Matt. 12:35<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">11. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108047\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108047)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108047)\">Matt. 13:52<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">12. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108027\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108027)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108027)\">Matt. 13:33<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">13. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109716\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109716)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109716)\">Gal. 1:12<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110653\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110653)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110653)\">Rev. 1:1<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114600\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114600)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114600)\">D&amp;C 84:1<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114976\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114976)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114976)\">D&amp;C 90:11<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116111\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116111)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116111)\">D&amp;C 128:8<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">14. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111438\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111438)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111438)\">Jacob 7:17<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112961\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112961)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112961)\">Moro. 7:25<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113223\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113223)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113223)\">D&amp;C 13:1<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113338\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113338)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113338)\">D&amp;C 20:10<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113817\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113817)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113817)\">D&amp;C 43:25<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"117142\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 117142)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(117142)\">JS&mdash;H 1:65<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">15. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109466\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109466)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109466)\">1 Cor. 5:6<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109744\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109744)\">&nbsp